metadata.name: ABADDON: A Story Told via AI #1/10
metadata.description:
Alone in the alleyways of New Orleans, a yellow jacket bobs down the alleyway, the scrawny legs creating a cartoonishly imposing shadow down the filth covered back way. His loose dreaded hair hangs coverings teary eyes. A man drunkenly bumps into the jacketed boy and 2 glowing eyes filled with a determined rage stare back.  
This is Abbadon “Don” Doucet and we’re 20 minutes away from his death.
